&lt;p&gt;Stock Hill Medical Centre is currently looking to welcome an experienced practice nurse to join the team at Stock Hill Medical Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a friendly and supportive practice with a list size of approx.. 10449&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Practice team includes 3 Partners, 4 Salaried GPs, 3 Nurses and 2 HCAs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are ideally looking for a nurse who has experience in chronic disease management, COPD and Asthma. Experience in diabetes would be advantageous.&lt;/p&gt;
